protected theorem unop_map_list_prod [Semiring R] [Semiring S] (f : «expr ≃+* » R («expr ᵐᵒᵖ» S)) (l : list R) :

  unop_map_list_prod f l
#align unop_map_list_prod unop_map_list_prod
-/
